<h2 class="call"><a name="setting-physical-uri">Setting physical URI</a></h2>

<p>
To connect the device to the physical device you need to fill the
<code>physical</code> field with the following URI structure
<code>http://nodes.lelylan.com/mqtt/&lt;device-id&gt;</code>,
where the device id is the one you are working at.
</p>

<h4>Example</h4>

<div class="preview">
<pre><code><span style="color: #999">device.id:</span>   518be5a700045e1521000001
<span style="color: #999">physical uri</span> http://nodes.lelylan.com/mqtt/518be5a700045e1521000001</pre></code>
</div>

